Package it.polimi.ingsw.View

Class ClientView

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.View.ClientView
All Implemented Interfaces:
ViewShowElement, VirtualView
public class ClientView extends Object implements VirtualView, ViewShowElement
This class represents the object used to store game information retrieved from the server. It makes use of Data Transfer Object (it.polimi.ingsw.DTO) pattern to keep track of the current state of game's elements.
